    <text type="letter">
        <body>

           
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="duk.00589.001.jpg" type="recto"/>
            
            <note type="editorial" resp="#rmb" place="top">24 March 1870</note>
            
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when="1870-03-24">24<ptr target="duk.00589_n8"/></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>O <choice><orig>walt</orig><reg>Walt</reg></choice></salute>
            </opener>
            
            <p><choice><orig>aint</orig> <reg>ain't</reg></choice> it sad
                to think the poor soul<ptr target="duk.00589_n11"/>
            
            <choice><orig>hadent</orig> <reg>hadn't</reg></choice> a friend near
            him in his last moments
            and to think he had a
            <choice><orig>paupers</orig> <reg>pauper's</reg></choice> grave i know
            it makes no difference
            but if he could have
            been buried decently
            but <choice><orig>hes</orig> <reg>he's</reg></choice> done poor
            fellow i was thinking
            of him more lately
            than common
            i wish <choice><orig>walter</orig><reg>Walter</reg></choice> you would
                write to Jeff<ptr target="duk.00422_n2"/> and <choice><orig>hann</orig><reg>Han</reg></choice><ptr target="duk.00438_n4"/>
            that he is dead i will
            write to <choice><orig>george</orig><reg>George</reg></choice><ptr target="duk.00425_n2"/> i feel
            very sad of course <choice><orig>walter</orig><reg>Walter</reg></choice>
            if he has done ever so 
            wrong he was my first
            born but <choice><orig>gods</orig> <reg>God's</reg></choice> will
            be done</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>good bie <choice><orig>walter</orig><reg>Walter</reg></choice> dear</salute>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="duk.00589.002.jpg" type="verso"/>
            <postscript><p>walter send me<ptr target="duk.00425_n3"/> one envelope next time you write</p></postscript>
        </body>
    </text>
